GPRacing_GameRule_Position_2_Pos_Detail: Number of 2nd car equal to selected number, between 1 to 10
GPRacing_GameRule_Position_2_BS_Detail: Number of 2nd car is bigger or equal to 6, is Big number. Smaller or equal to 5 is Small number.

GPRacing_GameRule_Position_3_Pos_Detail: Number of 3rd car equal to selected number, between number 1 to 10.

GPRacing_GameRule_Position_3_OE_Detail: Number of 3rd Car is odd or even number
GPRacing_GameRule_Sum_1_2_Detail: Sum of 1st & 2nd car equal to selected number, between number 3 to 19
GPRacing_GameRule_Sum_1_2_OE_Detail: Sum of 1st & 2nd car numbers are odd number or even number
GPRacing_GameRule_Sum_1_2_BS_Detail: Sum of 1st & 2nd car numbers are bigger then 11 is big, smaller or equal then 11 is small
GPRacing_GameRule_Sum_1_2_3_Detail: Sum of 1st, 2nd & 3rd car equal to selected number, between number 6 to 27
GPRacing_GameRule_Sum_1_2_3_OE_Detail: Sum of 1st, 2nd & 3rd car numbers are odd number or even number
GPRacing_GameRule_Sum_1_2_3_BS_Detail: Sum of 1st, 2nd & 3rd car numbers are bigger then 17 is big, smaller or equal then 17 is small
GPRacing_GameRule_DT_1_10_Detail: Number of 1st Car bigger then number of 10th Car is Dragon, if smaller is Tiger

GPRacing_GameRule_DT_4_7_Detail: Number of 4th Car bigger then number of 7th Car is Dragon, if smaller is Tiger
GPRacing_GameRule_DT_5_6_Detail: Number of 5th Car bigger then number of 6th Car is Dragon, if smaller is Tiger

Sicbo_GameRule_Wager_1: The total score will be from 11 to 17 (inclusive) with the exception of a triple
Sicbo_GameRule_Wager_2: The total score will be from 4 to 10 (inclusive) with the exception of a triple
Sicbo_GameRule_Wager_3: The total score will be an odd number with the exception of a triple
Sicbo_GameRule_Wager_4: The total score will be an even number with the exception of a triple
Sicbo_GameRule_Wager_5: Two of the dice will show a specific combination of two different numbers (for example, a 3 and a 4)
Sicbo_GameRule_Wager_8: Any three of the four numbers in one of the following specific combinations will appear: 6, 5, 4, 3; 6, 5, 3, 2; 5, 4, 3, 2; or 4, 3, 2, 1

Sicbo_GameRule_Wager_17: Two of the dice will show a specific double and the third die will show a specific, different number

Sicbo_GameRule_Wager_19: A specific number will appear on all three dice
4DLotto_GameRule_CustomBet_Detail: Select a set of 4 digit numbers from 0000 to 9999, then choose the bet type and bet. If the opening number match your 4 digit selection, you will win the amount as displayed
4DLotto_GameRule_Box_Detail: Select a set of 4 digit numbers from 0000 to 9999, then bet, all your bet will be multiply by number of rotation (i.e 1234 has 24 rotations, then 1 dollar bet will be multiply to 24 dollar bet). If the opening number match your selection, you will win the amount as displayed
4DLotto_GameRule_IBox_Detail: Select a set of 4 digit numbers from 0000 to 9999, then bet, all your bet will be devided by number of rotation (i.e 1234 has 24 rotations, then 1 dollar bet will be devided to 1/24 dollar bet). If the opening number match your selection, you will win the amount as displayed
4DLotto_GameRule_Quarter_Detail: Select a set of 4 digit numbers from 0000 to 9999, then bet, your bet amount will be devided by 4 (to be placed evenly in Big/Small/3A/C ). If the opening number match your selection, you will win the amount as displayed
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_4D3D2D_Standa: Select a set of 4 digit numbers (4D) from 0000 to 9999, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
Select a set of 3 digit numbers (3D) from 000 to 999, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
Select a set of 2 digit numbers (2D) from 00 to 99, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
If the opening number match your 4 digit selection, you will win the amount as displayed.
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_4D3D2D_QuickB: Key in a set of 4 digit numbers from 0000 to 9999, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
Key in a set of 3 digit numbers from 000 to 999, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
Key in a set of 2 digit numvbers from 00 to 99, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
If the opening number match your 4 digit selection, you will win the amount as displayed.
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_4D3D2D_BolakB: Key in a set of 4 digit numbers from 0 to 9, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet). Your bet will automatically bet for all 4digits 4D combinations, 3digits 3D combinations and 2 digits 2D combinations
for example - combination of 4digits (4D), 3digits (3D) and 2digits (2D) is 60 combinations, which is 24 combinations for 4digits (4D), 24 combinations for 3digits and 12 combinaitons for 2digits
If the opening number match your selection, you will win the amount as displayed.
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_4D3D2D_BBCamp: Key in a set of 4 to 9 digit numbers from 0 to 9, then fill the bet amount at 4D, 3D and 2D (submit to valid the bet). Your bet will automatically bet for all 4digits 4D combinations, 3digits 3D combinations and 2 digits 2D combinations yeild within the 4 to 9 digits numbers.

for example - 5digits set, combination of 4digits (4D), 3digits (3D) and 2digits (2D) within 5 digits of numbers is 200 combinations, whic h is 120 combinations for 4digits, 60 combinations for 3digits and 20 combinaitons for 2digits
If the opening number match your selection, you will win the amount as displayed
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_4D3D2D_Quick2: Select Big (50-99)/ Small (00-49)/ Odd/ Even for the 2 digits numbers at Front/ Back/ Middle, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
If the opening number match your 4 digit selection, you will win the amount as displayed.
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_4D3D2D_4DSet_: Key in a set of 4 digit numbers from 0000 to 9999, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet). Your bet will automatically bet for all 4digits, 3digits and 2digits from the 4 numbers you selected.
If the opening number match your selection, you will win the amount as displayed.
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_4D3D2D_2DDepa: Select a set of 2 digits number from 00 to 99 at front two position from the full 4digits, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
If the opening 1st Prize number match your 2digit selection, you will win the amount as displayed.
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_4D3D2D_2DTeng: Select a set of 2 digits numbers (2D) from 00 to 99 at middle two position of the full 4digits, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
If the opening 1st Prize number match your 2 digit selection, you will win the amount as displayed.
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_ColokBebas_De: Select a number between 0 to 9, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
If the opening 1st Prize numbers contain your selected number, you will win the amount as displayed
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_ColokBebas2D_: Select 2 different number between 0 to 9, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
If the opening 1st Prize numbers contain your selected number, you will win the amount as displayed
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_ColokNaga_Det: Select 3 different numbers between 0 to 9, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
If the opening 1st Prize numbers contain your selected number, you will win the amount as displayed
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_ColokJitu_Det: Select 1 number between 0 to 9, following by selecting its position (1st/2nd/3rd/4th number) then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
If your selected number matched the opening 1st Prize numbers at your selected position, you will win the amount as displayed
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_Tengah_Detail: Select Tengah (25 - 74)/ Tepi (00 - 24) (75 - 99) for last 2digits (2D), then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
If your selection matched the opening 1st Prize numbers, you will win the amount as displayed
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_Dasar_Detail_: Select Big (50 - 99)/ Small (00 - 49)/ Odd/ Even for the Sum of last 2digits (2D) numbers, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
If your selection matched the the Sum of last 2digits (2D) opening 1st Prize numbers, you will win the amount as displayed
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_5050_Detail_1: Select Big (50 - 99)/ Small (00 - 49)/ Odd/ Even for the 1st/2nd/3rd/4th number, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_5050_Detail_2: If your selection matched the the opening 1st Prize numbers at the right position, you will win the amount as displayed
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_50502D_Detail: Select Big (50 - 99)/ Small (00 - 49)/ Odd/ Even for the last 2digits, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
If your selected number matched the last 2 digits of opening 1st Prize numbers, you will win the amount as displayed
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_Shio_Detail_1: Select Rat/ Pig/ Dog/ Roaster/ Monkey/ Goat/ Horse/ Snake/ Dragon/ Rabbit/ Tiger/ Bull for the last 2digits, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_Shio_Detail_2: If your selected Shio matched the last 2digits of opening 1st Prize numbers, you will win the amount as displayed
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_Silang_Detail: Select Front 2digits, Middle 2digits or Back 2digits, bet for Silang (Odd + Even) or Homo (Odd + Odd or Even + Even),  then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
If your selection matched the opening 1st Prize numbers, you will win the amount as displayed
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_Kembang_Detai: Select Front 2digits, Middle 2digits or Back 2digits, bet for Kembang (1st number of 2digits bigger then 2nd number), Kempis (1st number of 2digits smaller then 2nd number) or Kembar (1st number and 2nd number of 2digits are the same),  then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
If your selection matched the opening 1st Prize numbers, you will win the amount as displayed
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_Kombinasi_ASK: Select Big (5-9)/ Small (0-4)/ Odd/ Even for 1st number of 4digits 4D), then select Big (5-9)/ Small (0-4)/ Odd/ Even for 2nd number of 4 digits 4D, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_Kombinasi_Kep: Select Big (5-9)/ Small (0-4)/ Odd/ Even for 3rd number of 4digits 4D), then select Big (5-9)/ Small (0-4)/ Odd/ Even for 4th number of 4digits 4D, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_Kombinasi_Com: Select 1st & 2nd numbers in Big/ Small/ Odd/ Even, then select 3rd & 4th numbers in Big/ Small/ Odd/ Even of 4digits 4D, then fill the bet amount (submit to valid the bet)
4DLotto_Indonesia_GameRule_Kombinasi_Det: If your selection matched the opening 1st Prize numbers, you will win the amount as displayed
HKLotto_GameRule_GrandJackpot_Detail_1: Select 6 numbers as 1 set (each set 3000idr), if all your number match the opened number in accordance to position 1 to 6, then you win the Grand Jackpot (if you are not the only winner, then you will share the Grand Jackpot pool equally with all other winners)
HKLotto_GameRule_GrandJackpot_Detail_2: * You can select your own lucky numbers or bet computer generated numbers
